'''Burntmeat''' is a [[troll]] featured in the quests [[Eadgar's Ruse]] and [[My Arm's Big Adventure]] . He can be found in the [[troll kitchen|Troll Stronghold kitchen]]. He is sometimes criticised by other trolls for only being able to cook [[burnt meat]]. Most trolls are named after the first thing they eat, however, Burntmeat was named after the first thing he tried to cook.

Burntmeat believes that he is a master chef, and after Eadgar's Ruse and My Arm's Big Adventure he gives the player a reward, burnt meat, which he claims is very valuable.

